## General settings related to Direct Messages

In**WP admin  Voxel  Settings  Direct messages** you can configure general settings related to the Direct messages feature in Voxel

### General

- Maximum message length (in characters)

### Uploads

- Enable file uploads
- Max file size (kB)
- Max file count
- Allowed file types

### Real-time

- Update chats in real-time
- Show seen badge

### Storage

- Delete messages older than (days)
